description: An ESOU operative is baffled when miles of newly made, underground passages located under the Valley of the Volcanoes in Peru are discovered. The ESOU travels to this area to follow-up the investigations, and soon realizes that an ancient doomsday prophecy is unfolding that will change the planet.
name: Dark World

description: The Doctor and company travel to the city of Casablanca to discover all is not as it seems. The city streets are filled with Nazis, Silurians and a familiar looking bar owner.
name: As Time Goes By Part 1

description: Deadpool's got a price on his head. And Agent X is about to cash in! Featuring the triumphant return of Crazy Inez, Deadpool's sane-again, insane-again girlfriend!
name: The X-Man

description:
When the gregarious Dollar Bill takes out an ad for new Defenders, heroes from all walks of life heed the call!

The real Defenders are swamped - but they might just need all the extra muscle to defeat the hordes of villains that have come out of the woodwork!
name: Membership Madness

description: Long ago, on the planet Cybertron... as dissident Decepticons rise up to battle the Autobot leadership, ORION PAX leads a counter-terror strike team. But when a routine mission goes awry, Orion starts on an incredible journey to the heart of Cybertron's Autocracy.
name: Law and Disorder

description: The vital backstory of iconic characters Dejah Thoris and Tars Tarkas that ties directly into the film's storyline continues here!
name: 4 of 4

volume.name: John Carter: The World of Mars

description: The Dreadlands are being corrupted by madness, causing its victims to open their flesh and lash out at friend and foe alike. Jacob, a young fugitive from the city of Staalbreak, may be Sanctuaryâs only hope to stop this plague before it consumes or destroys mankind. His destiny is bound to a mysterious sword and the woman who watches over it, but his own troubled soul may keep him from embracing its true power in time.
name: Sword of Justice

description: Jughead is heading to the Winter Resort with his best bud - Archie! Only problem is Jughead's pet Hot Dog was under the impression that that was him! Determined to confirm his role as Jug's best friend, Hot Dog pursues his master on vacation in hopes of earning his place as top dog!
name: Best Friends

description: Archie's best pal continues his search for a place to call homeâ¦ at least temporarily. After yet another living situation goes awry, Jughead finds shelter with Riverdale High's resident pop psychologist, Trula Twyst! Jughead hopes to use the opportunity for Trula to analyze him and sort out his family issues before he over stays his welcome! However, Jug may not be the only one taking advantage of his stay...
name: A Jughead in the Family Part 4: Psyche Out!

description: Jughead has burned a few bridges in his ongoing search for a place to lie his head which leads him to his last resort! Reggie invites Jughead to crash at his place in an attempt to alter his image after a girl turns him down for his bad rep. But will the unlikely duo be able to work past their trust issues and make their living arrangement work?
name: The Jug That Came in from the Cold!

description: Captain Hero battles the nefarious Witch Doctor who's up to no good! Captain Hero aligns himself with Pureheart the Powerful and Super Teen to outnumber the evildoer but using his ditto machine to duplicate himself, which Witch is real? See if our hero can figure it out in time before his super human appetite does him in!
name: Multiple Madness

volume.name: New Kids On The Block Chillin'

description:
Will Scrowlie survive the unknowable horror in the caverns beneath her spacious live/work loft? Why exactly does the evil lady want to destroy the world with her army of fashion zombies? And what does all this have to do with flappers and Black Tuesday?

Creators Jennifer Feinberg and Todd Meister.

description:
Still waiting for your prince to come? Tired of spending night after night locked in a secluded tower? Ready for your own adventure? So are we.

Princeless is the story of Princess Adrienne, one princess whoâs tired of waiting to be rescued. Join Adrienne and her guardian dragon, Sparky, as they begin their own quest in an all-ages action adventure designed specifically for those who are tired of waiting to be rescuedâ¦ and who are ready to save themselves.

Now that Princess Adrienne has escaped, itâs up to her to save her sisters. The first on her list is the youngest sister, Appalonia. But saving Appalonia means going back to her familyâs castle andâ¦even worseâ¦facing her father. Will Adrienne be able to break into her old home and if she does, will she be able to get out again?

Adrienne has hit a bump in the road. She has failed in her first attempt at rescuing one of her sisters. In fact, she didnât even make it out with her pants intact! No rest for the weary though, because now she must face every female action heroâs archenemy: fashion. Sheâs rescued herself from captivity in her tower, but can Adrienne escape the bonds of chain mail underwear and leather corsets?

As the horrific details of the Pickman case unfold Detective William Zhu finds himself immersed in a macabre world of occult terror. Zhu is driven by unseen forces into a confrontation with evil beyond anything he has ever encountered before. If Zhu is to survive this ordeal with his sanity intact he may be forced to take the law into his own hands and destroy the monster himself!

description:
Now THAT's customer service! Rebecca, the world's premier purveyor of feverish female-on-female flesh, fetish and fantasy, brings us an eager-to-please workforce of Sapphic suburban swingers. That's right, these Housewives are out of the house and bringing home the bacon -- but the sizzle's all on the job! As always, Rebecca's exquisitely explicit, lusciously lush tonal drawings make these pin-ups pop off the page with unparalleled passion.

Whether they're demonstrating a new mattress, pumping gas, showcasing a pearl necklace or serving up a tasty muffin -- sometimes wearing nothing but a nametag (ouch!) -- these bodacious bosses, bangin' baristas, libidinous lifeguards, horny hairdressers, and lascivious loan officers are stimulating their own economy and guaranteed to have your sales chart rising! For these women, complete customer satisfaction is their #1 goal!

description: Time-traveling hero Booster Gold investigates the death of Batman â only to run afoul of another Batman. And this Caped Crusader doesnât want Booster anywhere near this case. To prevent the murder of the Dark Knight, Booster will have to travel back in time, where he must first stop the mysterious Black Beetle from destroying the New Teen Titans â or will Deathstroke the Terminator get in the way? And if Booster fails, the next target on the Black Beetleâs kill list is the entire Justice League of America!

Convicted child killer Richard Pickman now rots in a cell at Heorot maximum security prison. Has the evil been contained? description: Italian collection of the issues narrating the Civil War saga
name: Civil War

description: The Abramovici twins, no longer conjoined, find themselves on separate sides of a smoldering feud between Joker and Penguin. But how will Joker react, considering only one twin should have survived?
name: Separation Anxiety (Part 3)

description: Robin goes solo in the start of this new, three-chapter storyline. Rumors of an underground fight club run by the Penguin lead Batman's partner to coin an alias and journey below Cobblepot's Iceberg Lounge. But the Boy Wonder is about to find himself in the middle of a heavyweight match between Bane and an even more frightening opponent.
name: Theatre Of Violence (Part 1)

description: Here is a tale of a beautiful princess who lives in a castle twelve stories high and can see for miles and miles. Wishing to marry a man more clever than herself, the princess decides that only a man that can hide himself from her will become her husband. Unfortunately, the royal magician turns all of the men that try to hide from her into marble statues. With the help of a raven, a fox and a fish, will the merchant be able to accomplish this task? Beautifully illustrated, this tale captures the imagination of readers of all ages and inspires a love of reading.
name: The Princess Who Saw Everything

description: A high-spirited tale of a resourceful soldier who unwittingly serves his king. Beautifully illustrated, this classic tale will capture children's interest and spark their imagination inspiring a lifelong love of literature and reading.
name: Brightboots

description: What happens when Deadpool crosses paths with royalty? Watch the madness unfold as the Merc with a Mouth finds out what it's like to cavort with two of Marvel's mightiest monarchs - of the Asgardian and Wakandan variety - as well as hanging with some crooked cronies more befitting his ill-mannered ilk. Guest-starring Thor, Loki, the Black Panther,Constrictor, Taskmaster and more! Collecting DEADPOOL (1997) #34-45 and BLACK PANTHER (1998) #23.
name: Volume Six

description: Loki is back, and the mystery surrounding his death is about to be revealed! Sadly, when he's the first to discover the dread secret behind Fear Itself and issues forth a call to arms, none in Asgard will heed him. Follow Loki to the very depths of hell as he wades through the dead to find someone to join his cause. But Loki will soon learn the dead do not forgive easily - or forget! What can the rejuvenated trickster god be up to this time? And how will it affect Thor? Acclaimed creators Kieron Gillen and Doug Braithwaite bring Thor's dark little brother back into the fray. It's time for the Odinson and the Trickster to reunite! Collecting Journey into Mystery (1952) #622-626, and material from Thor Spotlight and Fear Itself Spotlight.
name: TPB

description: When the Fear Itself hammer falls, the raft is destroyed by one of its most powerful prisoners with a newfound weapon of the gods! Hundreds of the most powerful criminals in the world are now on the loose. But their threat is nothing compared to that of the one man who was already unstoppable, and now wields godlike power. Now the Thunderbolts will begin to learn the true meaning of FEAR ITSELF! Collecting THUNDERBOLTS #158-162.
name: Fear Itself: Thunderbolts

description: Elves, Gods, and Over-Minds - oh my! What else can you expect when your team's starting lineup consists of a sorcerer, a gargoyle, a Valkyrie, a pair of X-Men, a former model, the Son of Satan, and more of Marvel's wildest warriors? Far out fantasy the likes you've never seen, that's what! Guest-Starring Odin, the New Mutants and more! Collecting DEFENDERS (1972) #122-124 and NEW DEFENDERS #125-131.
name: Volume One
